      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Honest poor-condition car being sold as-is. It has significant wear and age-related issues, and a buyer should expect cosmetic flaws, a tired interior, and mechanical needs rather than a clean turnkey vehicle. It may still run and drive, but it should be viewed as a project, fixer-upper, or parts candidate depending on your plans. Best for someone who knows what they\u2019re looking at and is prepared to put work into it.",
