      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of personality you just don\u2019t find in cookie-cutter commuters. It\u2019s an honest, hardworking machine with a seasoned presence and plenty of story left to write\u2014perfect for someone who wants an affordable set of wheels with charm, grit, and project potential. Whether you need a budget-friendly daily, a tinkering companion, or a practical car with character, this one offers a chance to get on the road without breaking the bank.",
      "price": 5900.0,
